Python Examples for AWS Infra-As-Code / API Control

Recommended installation steps for AWS / Python:
Install python pip and useful libraries:

apt-get -y install libcurl3 libcurl3-dev libssl-dev python-pip

Install aws command line interface and boto3 aws python library:

As root:
apt install awscli

As user:
pip install --upgrade --user awscli
pip install boto3

Make sure to configure AWS defaults by running as a user not as root:

As user:
aws configure

You can make a default region without the whole subregion i.e.:
region = us-east-2
